name: 25 STUNNING SCENIC DEPARTURES! Vancouver International Airport Plane Spotting
description:
Vancouver International Airport, or YVR, is the second busiest airport in Canada by passenger traffic. Vancouver itself is one of, if not the most scenic cities in the country, and on a clear sunny day with the North Shore Mountains in view, 26L departures from YVR look incredible!

Filmed from Terra Nova Park, with thanks to Brandon: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCWq8ksng53Nzi0iMA4_rE_w
